# Catppuccin Mocha theme for GNU dircolors
# Based on Bliss dircolors by @JoshJon, remapped to Catppuccin Mocha palette
#
# Palette:
#   Lavender: 183  |  Sky:     117  |  Green: 114
#   Peach:    209  |  Maroon:  204  |  Teal:  116
#   Surface0: 235  |  Surface1: 238 |  Overlay0: 245
#   Text:     189  |  Subtext:  248

# Term Section
TERM Eterm
TERM ansi
TERM color-xterm
TERM con132x25
TERM con132x30
TERM con132x43
TERM con132x60
TERM con80x25
TERM con80x28
TERM con80x30
TERM con80x43
